column4: NSLOCTEXT("[97758426423C295033B966895B803A66]", "4C1BA57549B5CB4420635FAB61DF206E", "Hi, I\'m busy all the time running this shop... Not!")
NSLOCTEXT("[97758426423C295033B966895B803A66]", "D59CC65142B77302B819FCA221FDFDA5", "I\'m kinda lazy and I won\'t be in the shop much. But I got some cool stuff.")
NSLOCTEXT("[97758426423C295033B966895B803A66]", "FB1210D049B621B10042DFB54B3A5B83", "Yes! \'Training Manual\'! With this, your training will get better!")
NSLOCTEXT("[97758426423C295033B966895B803A66]", "7B2C635341A23EEEF48684A89232724D", "It\'s very valuable. I\'ll sell it for fifty thousand bits. You\'ll regret not buying it.")
NSLOCTEXT("[97758426423C295033B966895B803A66]", "63ADBEEB4FDB1806291CD488E0EC660A", "Hmmm, you have lots of stuff with you.")
